<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَلَى أَخِيهِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> ، وَعِتْقِهِ عَلَيْهِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> ، وَفِي قَبُول شَهَادَتِهِ، وَفِي الْقَضَاءِ لَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">مَوَاطِنُ الْبَحْثِ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣ - بِالإِْضَافَةِ إِلَى مَا تَقَدَّمَ يَتَكَلَّمُ الْفُقَهَاءُ عَنِ الأَْخِ ضِمْنَ الأَْقَارِبِ فِي الْوَقْفِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَخٌ لأَِبٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> أَخٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَخٌ لأُِمٍّ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>.<span class="c5"> انْظُرْ:</span> أَخٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِخَالَةٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">التَّعْرِيفُ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ - الإِْخَالَةُ مَصْدَرُ أَخَال الأَْمْرُ أَيِ اشْتَبَهَ.<span class="c5"> وَيُقَال:</span> هَذَا الأَْمْرُ لاَ يُخِيل عَلَى أَحَدٍ، أَيْ لاَ يَشْكُل.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
